channel.title: My photoshop works- novice to proffesional
channel.description:
[IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/curtsigcopy.png[/img] this ones a tad bit overcontrasted god none the less i gave it to steph i couldnt put anytext without ruining the sig its self
[IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/fractals/aburningpassion.png[/img] a really good fractal i did about 3 months back
[IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/sigs/spidermansig1copy.png[/img] a sig of spiderman i did, was very pleased at outcome expect a tutorial n this style soon as i have seen no one able to iitate it correctly yet.
[IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/sigs/skylinemanip.png[/img] akyline photmanip, very good simple but elegant
[IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/sigs/665ca2d2.png[/img] rough unblended complex and beautiful. if i still had the psd for this, it would have a tutorial on it.
[IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/sigs/31f635d8.png[/img] the result of my being a smart ass to a moderator at sythe.org, if you cant figure out whom it was to, go die.
and finaly- the earliest work of mine still on the interweb- [IMG]http://i47.photobucket.com/albums/f170/kenokaze/sigs/tech.png[/img]
C&C on all if you want.
